mx-datetime (0.19.9.02) mx; urgency=medium

  * Hardware Clock no longer read at startup or reload.
  * Hide the buttons at the bottom in non-root mode.
  * Fixed: apparently missing time zones on systemd.
  * Improved detection of the init system.
  * Fixed truncated tool tip string.

